summary: A perfect hideout for assasins and thieves
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://s16.postimage.org/3le43rrmt/anisescabin.png[/img]

v1.0[/center]

* OVERVIEW *
My second character is an brutal assassin and thief and my \"house\" is the Anise\'s Cabin. I killed her and taken his cabin.
This mod adds some outfits like the archery targets, combat dummies and a coocking spit. Also it add a lantern to the cabin.
The lantern is lit from 6pm to 6am (15 minutes tolerance).

[center][img]http://s8.postimage.org/etec0jxo5/anise.jpg[/img][/center]

* INSTALL * 
Place the ESP and BSA in the data folder and activate the ESP.

* UNINSTALL *
Delete the ESP and BSA

* COMPATIBILITY *
This mod is safe. Does not modify anything, just adding new items (outfits).

* BUGS *
Please report to me if you find any bug or anomaly.
